Standing on
tradition,
building for
the future.
Standing on the rich history of our businesses, at Post Holdings, we’re dedicated to assembling our portfolio to be positioned to dynamically adapt to opportunities as they develop.















 

POST CONSUMER BRANDS US
postconsumerbrands.com
Post Consumer Brands is the third-largest cereal company in the United States with a broad portfolio spanning all segments of the category — from iconic household name brands and value ready-to-eat cereals to natural/organic and hot cereal varieties. As a company committed to high standards of quality and to our values, we are driven by one idea: To make better happen every day.


POST CONSUMER BRANDS CANADA
postconsumerbrands.ca
Post Consumer Brands Canada markets a broad portfolio of cereals — from iconic household name brands to value ready-to-eat cereals. As a company committed to high standards of quality and to our values, we are driven by one idea: To make better happen every day.


ATTUNE FOODS
attunefoods.com
At Attune Foods, what matters most is what’s inside. We believe if you use quality ingredients that are consistently crafted with care, what results is food that’s naturally delicious and nutritious. Attune Foods is your source for organic and Non-GMO granolas, cereals and snacks.


WEETABIX
weetabixfoodcompany.co.uk
Weetabix manufactures ready-to-eat cereal and is home to the UK’s number one selling cereal brand, Weetabix. An icon of British breakfast tables since 1932, we’ve made it our mission to delight consumers with great tasting, nutritious breakfasts produced with passion and excellence. At the core of our business, our purpose is to help people live better lives by providing better breakfasts.


MICHAEL FOODS
michaelfoods.com
At Michael Foods, our customers’ wants and needs serve as a foundation for all we do. We have become a leader in the food industry by introducing innovative, value-added customer solutions. We produce and distribute egg products to the foodservice, retail and food ingredient markets and refrigerated potato products to the foodservice and retail grocery markets.


DAKOTA GROWERS
dakotagrowers.com
Dakota Growers is a leading pasta manufacturer, providing over 150 pasta shapes, and innovative pasta formulas, for retail private label, foodservice and ingredient customers. Our entrepreneurial spirit drives the innovative culture, business integrity and passion to bring premium quality pasta to the table.


PREMIER NUTRITION
premiernutrition.com
Premier Nutrition manages a collection of brands, each of which is designed and positioned to deliver positive nutrition. Our products appeal to a wide range of people all looking to live healthy lives and needing the good energy to do so.


POWERBAR
powerbar.com
At PowerBar, our passion is to help you take pride in every step of the journey. Developed to help athletes from all walks of life recharge and refocus, our wide selection of products is crafted from simple ingredients, so you’re always ready, eating the best to give it your best.


DYMATIZE
dymatize.com
At Dymatize, we’re dedicated to perfecting athletic nutrition and committed to bringing you the most innovative and effective sports nutrition products. We produce a wide array of sports nutrition products, including our well-known whey protein isolate products.


GOLDEN BOY
goldenboyfoods.com
Golden Boy is a manufacturer, marketer and distributor of private label products, including organic and conventional peanut and other nut butters, baking nuts, raisins, other dried fruit and trail mixes. Our mission is to provide our customers with the highest quality products at the very best price while providing excellent customer support.

 





 




































 










 
 




